# Behavior Tree Asset for Dinosaur Combat AI
# This is a placeholder for the actual UE5 asset file
# The real asset would be created in the UE5 editor

# Behavior Tree Structure:
# Root
# ├── Selector (Combat Decision)
#     ├── Sequence (Retreat Behavior)
#     │   ├── Decorator: Check Fear > 0.7 OR Health < 25%
#     │   ├── Task: Find Safe Location (EQS)
#     │   └── Task: Move To Safe Location
#     ├── Selector (Active Combat)
#     │   ├── Sequence (Pack Attack)
#     │   │   ├── Decorator: Has Pack Members
#     │   │   ├── Task: Coordinate Pack Formation
#     │   │   └── Task: Execute Pack Attack
#     │   ├── Sequence (Ambush Attack)
#     │   │   ├── Decorator: Should Ambush AND Can Ambush
#     │   │   ├── Task: Move To Ambush Position (EQS)
#     │   │   ├── Task: Wait For Target
#     │   │   └── Task: Execute Ambush
#     │   ├── Sequence (Direct Attack)
#     │   │   ├── Decorator: Target In Attack Range
#     │   │   ├── Task: Face Target
#     │   │   └── Task: Attack Target
#     │   └── Sequence (Hunt Target)
#     │       ├── Decorator: Has Target
#     │       ├── Task: Find Optimal Attack Position (EQS)
#     │       └── Task: Move To Attack Position
#     ├── Sequence (Investigate)
#     │   ├── Decorator: Time Since Last Seen < 30s
#     │   ├── Task: Move To Last Known Location
#     │   └── Task: Search Area (EQS)
#     └── Sequence (Patrol)
#         ├── Task: Find Patrol Point (EQS)
#         ├── Task: Move To Patrol Point
#         └── Task: Wait At Patrol Point

# Key Blackboard Keys:
# - Target (Object): Current target actor
# - LastKnownTargetLocation (Vector): Last seen target position
# - Aggression (Float): Current aggression level (0-1)
# - Fear (Float): Current fear level (0-1)
# - IsInCombat (Bool): Whether currently in combat
# - CombatState (Enum): Current combat behavior state
# - PackMembers (Object Array): Current pack members
# - OptimalAttackPosition (Vector): Best position for attack
# - AmbushPosition (Vector): Position for ambush
# - SafeLocation (Vector): Retreat position